THE ROBOT SIMULATOR

It's small project created to simulate a robot tabletop.

SOLUTION

In order to conform with the requirements, my solution was to create two classes: Tabletop and Robot, which can simulate a robot moving on a tabletop and turning left and right.

TECHONOLOGY STACK

- Ruby

DEPENDENCIES

- RSpec

RUNNING THE TEST DATA

`bin/the_robot_simulator <file>`

bin/the_robot_simulator test_data/a
bin/the_robot_simulator test_data/b
bin/the_robot_simulator test_data/c

